.
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-config\fR:
.
.IP
The location of the config file\.
.
.TP
\fB\-\-custom\-dir\fR:
.
.IP
A directory to use for custom facts\.
.
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-debug\fR:
.
.IP
